bug.short_desc: Model does not get synced with input fields if Command activates button

long_desc.thetext: Created attachment 1053 application that demonstrates bug

A couple of additional comments:
Firstly, the command to flush the queue after calling ok.focus() is: qx.html.Element.flush()
Secondly, I think this whole thing is still broken. If qooxdoo allows attaching a keyboard command to a button, then pressing that keyboard sequence should do everything that clicking the button does. It should not require special code in the execute handler to deal with _how_ the execute handler got called (click or Enter)...
